Source String: This makes the lines of Walking Tours and Sightseeing Bus invisible. The line works, but you can't view or edit the path.
Translation: This makes the lines of Walking Tours and Sightseeing Bus invisible. The line works, but you can't view or edit the path.

Source String: This mod is suspected to sometimes prevent other mod buttons to show.
Translation: This mod is suspected to sometimes prevent other mod buttons to show.

Source String: Saving can take very long for maps with a high volume of trees and a large number of fires.
Translation: Saving can take very long for maps with a high volume of trees and a large number of fires.

Source String: This is missing all new item classes from all patches since release and from all DLCs.
Translation: This is missing all new item classes from all patches since release and from all DLCs.

Source String: This might need Ambient Sound Tuner 2.0: https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=818641631.
Translation: This might need Ambient Sound Tuner 2.0: https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=818641631.

Source String: This is missing statistics from later DLCs and game patches.
Translation: This is missing statistics from later DLCs and game patches.

Source String: Dropdown not working, probably due to incompatibility with other mods.
Translation: Выпадающий список не работает, вероятно, из-за несовместимости с другими модами.

Source String: Several functions are not working anymore and throws errors if you have not Industries DLC.
Translation: Several functions are not working anymore and throws errors if you have not Industries DLC.

Source String: Demand stays at zero.
Translation: Спрос остается на нуле.

Source String: Rocks can’t be deleted.
Translation: Rocks can’t be deleted.

Source String: Disable scrolling with one of the hotkeys before dezoning to prevent accidental massive dezoning. The same applies to other actions performed with the right mouse button, like road upgrades.
Translation: Отключите прокрутку с одной из горячих клавиш перед удалением зон, чтобы предотвратить случайное массовое удаление зон. То же самое относится и к другим действиям, выполняемым правой кнопкой мыши, например перестройкам дорог.

Source String: Part of the base game and the Paradox Launcher.
Translation: Part of the base game and the Paradox Launcher.

Source String: In resolutions other than 16:9 aspect ratio, it moves to the top left corner, blocking the default Infoview button.
Translation: В разрешениях, отличных от соотношения сторон 16:9, он перемещается в верхний левый угол, блокируя кнопку по умолчанию Infoview.

Source String: Images sometimes are only loaded if you restart the game and hotkeys also not work for all people.
Translation: Изображения иногда загружаются только если вы перезапустите игру и горячие клавиши также не работают для всех людей.

Source String: Not working for all buildings, performance issues, errors messages.
Translation: Не работает для всех зданий, проблемы с производительностью, сообщения об ошибках.

Source String: Conflicts with Metro Overhaul Mod pillar selection.
Translation: Конфликтует с выбором столбов Metro Overhaul Mod.

Source String: This has some issues with spaces in names.
Translation: This has some issues with spaces in names.

Source String: Deactivate the build in mods of Colossal Order, as the functions are included in Game Anarchy: Unlimited Money, Unlimited Oil And Ore, Unlock All. Take care to activate the functions before loading into a save.
Translation: Деактивируйте встроенные модификации Colossal Order, так как эти функции входят в Game Anarchy: Unlimited Money, Unlimited Oil And Ore, Unlock All. Постарайтесь включить функции перед загрузкой сохранения.

Source String: Be aware that this mod is instable and crashes may occur in larger cities!
Translation: Имейте в виду, что этот мод нестабилен и могут произойти ошибки в больших городах!

Source String: Seems to be a Traffic Manager clone, but tells it is Auto Line Color and the sourcecode is not available.
Translation: Seems to be a Traffic Manager clone, but tells it is Auto Line Color and the sourcecode is not available.

Source String: Various players report, information could not be gathered.
Translation: Various players report, information could not be gathered.

Source String: It’s in early development stage. See information on workshop page.
Translation: Ранний этап разработки. Смотрите информацию на странице в Мастерской.

Source String: Cargo trains for some do not spawn.
Translation: Для некоторых грузовые поезда не появляются.

Source String: Deactivate the build in Unlimited Soil mod of Colossal Order, as its function is included in Extra Landscaping Tools.
Translation: Деактивируйте встроенный мод Unlimited Soil от Colossal Order, так как эта функция входит в Extra Landscaping Tools.

Source String: Hide It Bobby can do all what No Radioactive can, except the tree color.
Translation: Hide It Bobby может сделать все, что есть No Radioactive, кроме цвета дерева.

Source String: The copy feature from Move It can also duplicate unique buildings.
Translation: The copy feature from Move It can also duplicate unique buildings.

Source String: The warehouse does not empty for some users. This might be caused by fishing boats taking up all vehicle slots, so no warehouse truck can spawn. Users have noticed trucks transferring fish from one warehouse to another.
Translation: The warehouse does not empty for some users. This might be caused by fishing boats taking up all vehicle slots, so no warehouse truck can spawn. Users have noticed trucks transferring fish from one warehouse to another.

Source String: This mod only works on Windows, not on MacOS or Linux. This is an advanced mod that requires Python scripting knowledge to use.
Translation: This mod only works on Windows, not on MacOS or Linux. This is an advanced mod that requires Python scripting knowledge to use.

Source String: Left hand traffic is not supported. This does not work on Linux. Opposite side traffic lights have some quirks on T-intersections and one-way roads.
Translation: Трафик с левосторонним движением не поддерживается. Не работает на Linux. Противоположные боковые светофоры имеют некоторые аномалии на Т-образных перекрестках и односторонних дорогах.

Source String: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. This mod is suspected of having malicious code in it. You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! WARNING: DON'T follow the instructions on the mod page to download an update through GitHub. That updater contains MALICIOUS code and will insert malicious code into this Harmony mod! The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Technically, this doesn't function very well, gives a lot of misguided errors and is incompatible with a lot of mods in the Workshop. Combined with the history of the author, it would be very wise to UNSUBSCRIBE!
Translation: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. This mod is suspected of having malicious code in it. You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! WARNING: DON'T follow the instructions on the mod page to download an update through GitHub. That updater contains MALICIOUS code and will insert malicious code into this Harmony mod! The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Technically, this doesn't function very well, gives a lot of misguided errors and is incompatible with a lot of mods in the Workshop. Combined with the history of the author, it would be very wise to UNSUBSCRIBE!

Source String: Long station names or duplicate station names might break the layout. Lines which serve the same station multiple times might confuse the mod. Station names on multi-platform stations might be incorrect.
Translation: Длинные названия станций или дублирующие названия станций могут нарушить разметку. Линии, обслуживающие одну и ту же станцию несколько раз, могут путать с мод. Имена станций, на многоплатформенных станциях могут быть неправильными.

Source String: Information on the Workshop for this is very limited, but seems to indicate this works. It takes some in-game time for the extra money to arrive.
Translation: Информация в Мастерской весьма ограничена, но похоже есть данные что мод работает. Для получения дополнительных денег потребуется некоторое время в игре.

Source String: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Technically, this might function. Considering the history of the author, it would be very wise to UNSUBSCRIBE!
Translation: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Technically, this might function. Considering the history of the author, it would be very wise to UNSUBSCRIBE!

Source String: Not working with delivery vehicles from the Industries and Sunset Harbor DLCs. Settings menu getting messed up (close and reopen settings might help). Potentially incompatible with all mods that modify the Vehicle AI.
Translation: Не работает с транспортными средствами доставки из DLC Industries и DLC Sunset Harbor. Меню настроек (закрытие и повторное открытие настроек) потенциально несовместимо со всеми модами, модифицирующими ИИ автомобилей.

Source String: Some users still get it to work, but for many it is partially or totally broken, including not being able to load a game save. Disabling the "new algorithm for unclogging traffic jams near outside connections" might help. Deleting the EnhancedDistrictServices.cgs file might also help, but you will lose all customizations.
Translation: Some users still get it to work, but for many it is partially or totally broken, including not being able to load a game save. Disabling the "new algorithm for unclogging traffic jams near outside connections" might help. Deleting the EnhancedDistrictServices.cgs file might also help, but you will lose all customizations.

Source String: There is a bug with spawning as a cow. Slopes, ramps and elevated paths don't seem to work. Some can only walk backwards or are floating.
Translation: There is a bug with spawning as a cow. Slopes, ramps and elevated paths don't seem to work. Some can only walk backwards or are floating.

Source String: This mod is not optimized and can cause performance issues. This probably has unknown incompatibilities with other mods.
Translation: This mod is not optimized and can cause performance issues. This probably has unknown incompatibilities with other mods.

Source String: If you have issues with font display, disable Custom Font Manager in the mod options.
Translation: Если у вас возникли проблемы с отображением шрифтов, отключите Custom Font Manager в настройках мода.

Source String: If intersections look blue, go into the mod's settings and enable auto-refresh. This increases loading time if you have many custom roads.
Translation: Если развязки выглядят синим, зайдите в настройки мода и включите авто-обновление. Это увеличивает время загрузки, если у вас много пользовательских дорог.

Source String: Unsubscribe after use! This will spam the game log and seriously increase the size.
Translation: Unsubscribe after use! This will spam the game log and seriously increase the size.

Source String: Severe drop in FPS when creating roads. Some users get an 'invalid shape' error. Reversing direction sometimes gives an exception. The exception is harmless, but you can't reverse that segment and have to delete and recreate.
Translation: Severe drop in FPS when creating roads. Some users get an 'invalid shape' error. Reversing direction sometimes gives an exception. The exception is harmless, but you can't reverse that segment and have to delete and recreate.

Source String: Increased loading time and memory usage. Short prop rendering distance.
Translation: Увеличено время загрузки и использование памяти. Короткое расстояние рендеринга объектов.

Source String: Grass might grow through CSUR roads. Hiding the grass with Hide It or raising the nodes slightly with Move It will help. Roads might sometimes be placed slightly below the surface. Raise them with Move It. Tunnel entrances from non-centered CSUR roads get covered by terrain. Some users report game crashes and CSUR interface not working.
Translation: Трава может вырастать через дороги CSUR. Скрывайте траву с помощью Hide It или слегка поднимайте узлы с помощью Move It. Дороги иногда могут быть слегка возвышены над поверхностью. Поднимите их с помощью Move It. Входы туннеля из нецентрированных CSUR дорог покрываются землями. Некоторые пользователи сообщают, что игра ломается, а CSUR интерфейс не работает.

Source String: Reported massive issues including: missing road textures, KeyNotFoundException error, game crashes, high memory usage.
Translation: Reported massive issues including: missing road textures, KeyNotFoundException error, game crashes, high memory usage.

Source String: Button missing. Error popups.
Translation: Кнопка отсутствует. Появляется ошибка.

Source String: This often blocks the road upgrade button. The scaling feature is broken and should not be used. Users are reporting some other issues as well.
Translation: This often blocks the road upgrade button. The scaling feature is broken and should not be used. Users are reporting some other issues as well.

Source String: Errors on startup. Missing UI. Performance issues (fps drops).
Translation: Ошибки при запуске. Отсутствует пользовательский интерфейс. Проблемы с производительностью (падает fps).

Source String: Hotkey not working (try left shift instead of right shift). Light settings of Ultimate Eyecandy resetting or the light getting very dark on any change in Relight settings, or at game loading.
Translation: Горячая клавиша не работает (попробуйте левый Shift вместо правого Shift). Световые настройки Ultimate Eyecandy сброшены или свет становится очень темным при любых изменениях в настройках Relight или при загрузке игры.

Source String: Screen flashes / flickering. Time jumping or going backwards.
Translation: Screen flashes / flickering. Time jumping or going backwards.

Source String: Several users report colors resetting when reloading a game. Copy-pasting colors from one prop to another doesn't (always) work.
Translation: Several users report colors resetting when reloading a game. Copy-pasting colors from one prop to another doesn't (always) work.

Source String: Showing the wrong type of traffic light when using 'Large Avenue with Grass'. It might not work for left hand traffic (LHT) and for small one-way roads or roads with trams.
Translation: Showing the wrong type of traffic light when using 'Large Avenue with Grass'. It might not work for left hand traffic (LHT) and for small one-way roads or roads with trams.

Source String: On some intersections duplicate traffic lights appear. On a T-intersection, no light appears on the intersecting road. Highways and highway ramps have the traffic lights on the wrong side of the intersection.
Translation: On some intersections duplicate traffic lights appear. On a T-intersection, no light appears on the intersecting road. Highways and highway ramps have the traffic lights on the wrong side of the intersection.

Source String: This mod can have an impact on game performance. Does not work in scenario games.
Translation: This mod can have an impact on game performance. Does not work in scenario games.

Source String: Errors in the game log about unallowed actions. Buses not spawning. No first names being assigned.
Translation: Ошибки в журнале игры о недопустимых действиях. Автобусы не появляются. Никаких имён не назначено.

Source String: Some users report this to cause unloadable games. It's unknown if this is a mod conflict or an issue with game patch 1.14. Some users report a missing UI. LODs can't be replaced. See the Workshop for more details about known issues.
Translation: Some users report this to cause unloadable games. It's unknown if this is a mod conflict or an issue with game patch 1.14. Some users report a missing UI. LODs can't be replaced. See the Workshop for more details about known issues.

Source String: Setting maintenance price is not working correctly. Try pressing Enter after setting a new price instead of using the Apply button. Vehicle settings such as capacity and speed cannot be set. Use the Advanced Vehicle Options mod for this instead.
Translation: Setting maintenance price is not working correctly. Try pressing Enter after setting a new price instead of using the Apply button. Vehicle settings such as capacity and speed cannot be set. Use the Advanced Vehicle Options mod for this instead.

Source String: Being unable to export with an 'XML root element missing' error in the log. Train tracks sometimes not included.
Translation: Невозможно выполнить экспорт с ошибкой «Отсутствует корневой элемент XML» в журнале. Железнодорожные пути иногда не включены.

Source String: The mod options screen might break if you have too many train assets. Some users report issues with config file not being properly created. This might cause some lag if not using FPS Booster.
Translation: The mod options screen might break if you have too many train assets. Some users report issues with config file not being properly created. This might cause some lag if not using FPS Booster.

Source String: This only works for displays with an aspect ratio of 16:9 or 16:10. This is missing functionality for more recent patches and DLCs.
Translation: This only works for displays with an aspect ratio of 16:9 or 16:10. This is missing functionality for more recent patches and DLCs.

Source String: Missing UI. Performance issues (fps drops).
Translation: Отсутствует UI. Проблемы производительности (снижается fps).

Source String: The International Airport of After Dark causes issues on line creation. There are some reports about a missing icon/button.
Translation: The International Airport of After Dark causes issues on line creation. There are some reports about a missing icon/button.

Source String: It produces 'duplicate prefab' errors, which are harmless. Some users report that traffic light props still turn white after the last update that should have fixed this.
Translation: Приводит к ошибкам "duplicate prefab", которые безвредны. Некоторые пользователи сообщают, что опоры светофора по-прежнему становятся белыми после последнего обновления, которое должно было это исправить.

Source String: Either toggle anarchy off or bulldoze trees/rocks before placing anything, to prevent trees/rocks in buildings or roads. To prevent props/trees from disappearing after loading a game, set this mod options to 'Anarchy ON by default'.
Translation: Выключите анархию или удаление деревьев/камней, прежде чем размещать что-нибудь, для предотвращения совмещения деревьев/камней в зданиях или дорогах. Чтобы не допустить исчезновения объектов/деревьев после загрузки игры, установите этот параметр 'Анархия ВКЛ по умолчанию'.

Source String: Applying a list will disable unneeded mods but not unsubscribe them, and disabled mods can cause issues. Assets that are included with a mod might glitch. Game settings resetting when saving this mods data.
Translation: Применение списка отключит ненужные моды, но не отпишет от них, и отключенные моды могут вызвать проблемы. Объекты, включенные в мод, могут глючить. Настройки игры сбрасываются при сохранении данных модов.

Source String: This does work for some corrupted game saves, but not for all. If the game save loads, the game will freeze for some time. This is normal.
Translation: This does work for some corrupted game saves, but not for all. If the game save loads, the game will freeze for some time. This is normal.

Source String: This causes severe lag when opening menu panels. Park panels sometimes become corrupted, requiring a game restart.
Translation: This causes severe lag when opening menu panels. Park panels sometimes become corrupted, requiring a game restart.

Source String: Custom pillars might reset on next load. UI for the mod not fully working.
Translation: Пользовательские столбы могут быть сброшены при следующей загрузке. Пользовательский интерфейс мода работает не полностью.

Source String: This is said to be broken, but there are quite some reports saying it works. You might need to set a 180 degress offset for the sun to properly go from east to west.
Translation: This is said to be broken, but there are quite some reports saying it works. You might need to set a 180 degress offset for the sun to properly go from east to west.

Source String: Bloom settings not being applied. Config files not loading.
Translation: Цветовые настройки не применяются. Конфигурационные файлы не загружаются.

Source String: This seems to work for some people, but others report issues. Doesn't work in the main menu, only works after loading a map.
Translation: This seems to work for some people, but others report issues. Doesn't work in the main menu, only works after loading a map.

Source String: You cannot save the generated roads and therefore you shouldn't open a save where it has been used afterwards. This mod is still in an early state of development.
Translation: You cannot save the generated roads and therefore you shouldn't open a save where it has been used afterwards. This mod is still in an early state of development.

Source String: This might cause cims to get stuck at broken or deleted public transport stops. This causes lag in larger cities.
Translation: This might cause cims to get stuck at broken or deleted public transport stops. This causes lag in larger cities.

Source String: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. This mod is suspected of having malicious code in it. You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite.
Translation: WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. This mod is suspected of having malicious code in it. You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite.

You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Translation: WARNING: This mod is DANGEROUS! It downloads files from an unmonitored location and overwrites the files of other mods with it. This is VERY DANGEROUS software and should not be used! You'd better REMOVE IT IMMEDIATELY! WARNING: This author was banned for putting malicious code in their mods. The author is also known for deliberately breaking their own mods out of spite. Source String: Network Anarchy supersede several mods and includes way more functionalities.
Translation: Network Anarchy скрывает несколько модов и включает в себя более функциональные возможности.
